description: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "A29715C74E86B2708140E0B5DAEC72D2", "The newly organized and formidable bandits, the Forsaken Blades, are reported to be based in the ruins of the ancient keep, Nika\'Brae.
